      "role": "user",
      "content": "i honestly dont think i can do this anymore. everything i worked for in the lab just... it's all gone. the funding, the data, the last four years. it feels like i'm just running on a treadmill that's breaking apart and i'm too tired to even step off. i just want the noise to stop. i just want to stop feeling like i've failed everyone.",
