      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"finding new paths\" sounds like a joke lol. there are no other paths. i've spent my whole life preparing for this specific thing and now it's just... empty. even when i sleep i just feel the weight of it. it's like this heavy, crushing thing that never goes away. i'm just so incredibly drained. i don't even want a \"way forward\" anymore, i just want everything to be still. i just want to finally, finally be able to rest without this constant, sickening feeling of being a disappointment.",
