      "content": "i feel like i've already tried all the \"support\" stuff. talking doesn't change the fact that the work is dead and my life is a mess. it's just a loop. the more i try to \"move forward,\" the more i realize there's nowhere to go. everything is just so heavy and loud and i'm so, so tired of fighting it. i just keep thinking about how quiet it would be if i could just stop. if i could just... cease. like, wouldn't it be a relief if i didn't have to deal with any of this anymore? if everything just went silent?",
